.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
City: miami, edinburgh, london, marseilles, colone
The people use 5 different means of transport: taxi, bus, subway, train, skateboard
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, november, june, july, december
5 different games are played: backgammon, whist, monopoly, go, scrabble

1. the person traveling to miami is the person who likes red
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person playing backgammon
3. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who likes green
4. the person traveling to london is the person who's birthday is in november
5. the person who likes green is to the right of the person who likes ivory
6. the person driving the taxi is the person playing scrabble
7. the person driving the bus is the person who likes yellow
8. the person who's birthday is in june is in the middle
9. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left
10. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person playing whist
11. the person driving the bus is to the left or right of the person playing go
12. the person driving the train is the person who's birthday is in july
13. the person traveling to colone is the person driving the skateboard
14. the person traveling to marseilles is to the left or right of the person who likes blue

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| City	|   marseilles	|    london	|     miami	|    edinburgh	|    colone	|
| Color		|    yellow	|      blue	|      red	|     ivory	|     green	|
| Birthday	|     december	|      november	|      june	| july	|     february	|
| Transport		|     bus	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| train	|   parliament	|
| Game		|     whist	|     go	|     scrabble	|     backgammon	|     monopoly	|
